Cng ty l n v ng u v nng lc, cng nghtrong lnh vc dch v cin cng trnh. companyInfo.notes:
- Ngy 18/11/1977: tin thn ca cng ty l Xng c kh Ph Lm c thnh lp.

- Ngy 01/04/1993: Cng ty K ngh Lnh (SEAREFICO) c thnh lp theo Quyt nh s 95/TS/QTC l doanh nghip nh nc loi 1 trc thuc Tng cng ty Xut nhp khu Thy sn Vit Nam (Seaprodex Vietnam).

- T thng 11/1996: B Thy sn ra quyt nh sp nhp X nghip C in Lnh Nng (SEAREE) thuc Cng ty Thy sn Min trung (Seaprodex Danang) vo Cng ty K ngh Lnh trc thuc Tng cng ty Thy sn Vit Nam.

- Nm 1999: Cng ty K ngh Lnh c c phn ha vi vn iu l 12 t ng v i tn thnh Cng ty C phn K ngh Lnh, gi nguyn tn giao dch l SEAREFICO (Nh nc nm gi 20% vn iu l, phn cn li ca cn b cng nhn vin Cng ty v cc c ng bn ngoi).

- Thng 02/2007: Tng vn iu l ln 23.97 t ng.

- Thng 11/2007: Tng vn iu l ln 46.36 t ng.

- Thng 05/2008: Tng vn iu l ln 80.2 t ng.

- Ngy 21/10/2009: nim yt v giao dch c phiu SRF ti HOSE.

- Nm 2010: Thnh lp cng ty con ARICO vi 100% vn u t ca SEAREFICO.

- Thng 11/2011: Tng vn iu l ln 81.32 t ng.

- Nm 2012: Thnh lp Chi nhnh c in cng trnh SEAREFICO M&E.

- Thng 12/2013: Tng vn iu l ln 162.54 t ng.

- Thng 04/2014: Tng vn iu l ln 243.74 t ng.

- Thng 07/2017: Tng vn iu l ln 324.95 t ng.

- Thng 12/2022: Tng vn iu l ln 355.66 t ng.
